title: Statement on Airstrike in Syria that Killed Sanafi al-Nasr (US Department of Defense)
text: ( Source : US Department of Defense ) Pentagon Press Secretary Peter Cook provided the following statement: On Oct. 15, Coalition forces conducted an airstrike in northwest Syria that killed Abdul Mohsen Adballah Ibrahim al Charekh, aka Sanafi
